| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5511 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8c4577be-4975-503d-bad9-75e8eb46b7e2"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
